When suggesting calorie targets for weig: When suggesting calorie targets for weight change, LiftLog assumes 7700 kcal per kilogram (3500 kcal per pound) of weight change distributed across the week. You can adjust this number at any time. Consider recalculating it if your activity level or goals change.
